            "text": "{\"schema\":{\"name\":\"sitemodalcontainer\",\"version\":\"1.0.0\"},\"meta\":{\"name\":\"esperanto/homepage/privacy\",\"versionKey\":11},\"data\":{\"modals\":[{\"schema\":{\"name\":\"kdsmodal\",\"version\":\"1.0.0\"},\"data\":{\"authenticationType\":\"unauthenticated\",\"modalName\":\"terms_policy_update_notification\",\"headingText\":\"Improving Your Experience\",\"kind\":\"base\",\"children\":[{\"schema\":{\"name\":\"text\",\"version\":\"1.0.0\"},\"data\":{\"text\":\"<p>To provide and personalize our offerings, make recommendations, detect and prevent fraud, and improve our services, we use tools that collect and record your data, which may include your searches for and purchases of health and wellness products. We also may share non-sensitive data with third parties, such as advertising and analytics vendors, social networks, technology providers, and research providers. By continuing to use our websites and apps and shop our stores, this means you consent to these practices and accept our <a href=\\\"/i/terms/website-and-app\\\" target=\\\"_self\\\" data-omnitureTag=\\\"Kroger Terms and Conditions\\\" aria-label=\\\"Kroger Terms and Conditions\\\">Terms</a> and our <a href=\\\"/i/privacy-policy\\\" target=\\\"_self\\\" data-omnitureTag=\\\"Kroger Privacy Policy\\\" aria-label=\\\"Kroger Privacy Policy\\\">Privacy Policy</a>.</p>\"},\"meta\":{\"name\":\"esperanto/privacy\",\"versionKey\":5}}],\"path\":[\"/\",\"/*\"]},\"meta\":{\"name\":\"esperanto/privacy\",\"versionKey\":4}}],\"overrides\":[\"/i/terms\",\"/i/privacy-policy\"]}}"
